 is written into `frontend/src/lib/api/` and should be committed together with backend API changes.\n+\n+## Development Environment\n+\n+The project runs as a split local environment:\n+\n+- PostgreSQL is hosted in Docker via `docker compose`.\n+- Backend runs with live reload using Air.\n+- Frontend runs with Vite dev server.\n+\n+Useful commands from the `Makefile`:\n+\n+- Start only PostgreSQL in Docker: `make run-pg-dev`\n+- Start backend only: `make run-backend-dev`\n+- Start frontend only: `make run-frontend-dev`\n+- Start full local environment: `make run-dev`\n+- Stop full local environment: `make stop-dev`\n+- Stop services individually: `make stop-pg-dev`, `make stop-backend-dev`, `make stop-frontend-dev`\n+\n+## Production Build Artifacts\n+\n+For production deployment, the repository builds and ships these artifacts:\n+\n+- Backend executable: `bin/server`\n+  - Built by `make build-backend-prod` (linux/amd64, with stripped symbols).\n+- Frontend static bundle: `frontend/dist/`\n+  - Built by `make build-frontend-prod APP_BASE_URL=https://yourdomain.com`.\n+- Full production bundle: both of the above via `make build-prod APP_BASE_URL=https://yourdomain.com`.\n+- Database migration SQL scripts in `sql/`\n+  - Regenerated by `make build` (via `make generate`) and used for production schema rollout.\n+\n+The `make deploy` target builds production artifacts, syncs `bin/server` and `frontend/dist/` to the server, and restarts the systemd service.\n+\n+## Versioning\n+\n+This project uses **Semantic Versioning** (`MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH`) stored in the root `version` file.\n+\n+- Policy:\n+  - `MAJOR`: breaking changes\n+  - `MINOR`: backward-compatible feature additions\n+  - `PATCH`: backward-compatible fixes\n+- Mechanism:\n+  - The current version is embedded into backend builds via Go linker flags.\n+  - Release tags are created as `vX.Y.Z`.\n+- Command:\n+  - `make bump BUMP=patch` (or `minor`, `major`)\n+\n+`make bump` updates the `version` file, creates a commit, and creates the corresponding git tag.\n*** End Patch"},"tool_use_id":"call_OyX2WcyFYGDPKhXUp9pcdCOS__vscode-1773995048432","cwd":"/home/alexl70/src/pet/linkshortener"}

